[SIZE=5][COLOR=#2ecc71][B]JExVote[/B][/COLOR] — [COLOR=#95a5a6]The Votifier Reward System[/COLOR][/SIZE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#bdc3c7]Built-in Votifier server · Vote streaks · Reward system · Beautiful GUIs · Multi-language[/COLOR][/SIZE]

[SIZE=2][COLOR=#e74c3c]Supports Votifier v1 (RSA) and NuVotifier v2 (HMAC) — no external Votifier plugin required.[/COLOR][/SIZE]

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
[/CENTER]

[SIZE=4][COLOR=#2ecc71]■[/COLOR] [B]What is JExVote?[/B][/SIZE]

JExVote handles everything related to server voting — from receiving votes off voting sites to rewarding players, tracking streaks, and displaying statistics. It ships with its own Votifier-compatible server built in, so you do not need NuVotifier or any other listener plugin. Just point your vote sites at the configured port and JExVote takes care of the rest.

Votes trigger configurable rewards, feed into a streak system that keeps players coming back, and populate a leaderboard GUI accessible to every player. Admins get full control through commands and hot-reloadable configuration files.


[SIZE=4][COLOR=#2ecc71]■[/COLOR] [B]Feature Overview[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Built-in Votifier server[/B] — Supports both v1 (RSA-encrypted) and v2 (HMAC-SHA256) protocols out of the box. No NuVotifier dependency.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]12 reward types[/B] — Commands, items, XP, currency (JExEconomy), permissions (LuckPerms), sounds, particles, titles, teleports, composite bundles, choice menus, and custom handler hooks.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Vote streaks[/B] — Tracks consecutive daily votes with configurable timeout. Milestone rewards at any day threshold you define.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Per-site rewards[/B] — Assign bonus rewards for specific vote sites on top of the default reward set.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Offline vote queue[/B] — Votes received while a player is offline are stored and delivered on next login.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Interactive GUIs[/B] — Vote overview, paginated leaderboard, and streak progress — all accessible with [ICODE]/vote[/ICODE].
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Vote site cooldowns[/B] — Rolling window or fixed daily reset per site. Players see exactly when they can vote again.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Vote points[/B] — Each site awards configurable points. Points are tracked separately from vote count.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Broadcast & private messages[/B] — Announce votes server-wide (all / others / none) with anti-spam cooldown, plus optional private thank-you messages.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Multi-language[/B] — Ships with English, German, Czech, and Slovak translations. Add your own or override existing ones.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Record retention[/B] — Automatically purges old vote records after a configurable number of days.
[*][COLOR=#2ecc71]✦[/COLOR] [B]Folia compatible[/B] — Scheduled tasks run through FoliaLib for full Folia support.
[/LIST]


