[SIZE=4][COLOR=#3498db]■[/COLOR] [B]GUIs[/B][/SIZE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#3498db]Vote Overview[/COLOR][/SIZE]

The main menu players see when they type [ICODE]/vote[/ICODE]. Shows their personal stats, a progress bar for the current streak, all configured vote sites with clickable links, and navigation to the leaderboard and streak views.

[CENTER]
[IMG]PLACEHOLDER_2_OVERVIEW — Screenshot of the Vote Overview GUI (6-row chest, emerald header, player head with stats, vote site buttons, navigation row)[/IMG]
[/CENTER]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#3498db]Leaderboard[/COLOR][/SIZE]

A paginated all-time leaderboard with player heads for the top 3. Each entry displays total votes, monthly votes, streak, vote points, and a visual vote bar. Navigate pages with the arrow buttons.

[CENTER]
[IMG]PLACEHOLDER_3_LEADERBOARD — Screenshot of the Leaderboard GUI (top 3 as player heads with gold/silver/bronze gradients, remaining entries below, page navigation)[/IMG]
[/CENTER]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#3498db]Streak Rewards[/COLOR][/SIZE]

Shows the player's current streak, highest streak, and all configured milestones. Achieved milestones glow green, the next target is highlighted yellow, and locked milestones are red. A 20-segment progress bar shows how close the player is to the next reward.

