[/CENTER]


[SIZE=4][COLOR=#9b59b6]■[/COLOR] [B]Reward Types[/B][/SIZE]

All 12 reward types and their configuration keys:

[SPOILER="Full Reward Reference"]
[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]command[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Executes a server command. Use [ICODE]{player}[/ICODE] as a placeholder for the player name.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: command
  command: "give {player} diamond 1"
  as-console: true     # true = run from console, false = run as player
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]item[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Gives an item stack with optional display name, lore, and enchantments.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: item
  material: DIAMOND_SWORD
  amount: 1
  name: "<gradient:#FFD700:#FFA500>Vote Blade</gradient>"
  lore:
    - "<gray>Rewarded for voting"
  enchantments:
    sharpness: 3
    unbreaking: 2
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]xp[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Grants vanilla experience points (not levels).
[CODE=YAML]
- type: xp
  amount: 100
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]currency[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Deposits money through JExEconomy. Requires the JExEconomy plugin.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: currency
  currency: "coins"
  amount: 500
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]permission[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Grants a permission node via LuckPerms. Supports timed and server-specific permissions.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: permission
  permission: "essentials.fly"
  duration: "7d"       # Optional — omit for permanent
  server: "survival"   # Optional — omit for global
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]sound[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Plays a sound effect at the player's location.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: sound
  sound: ENTITY_PLAYER_LEVELUP
  volume: 1.0
  pitch: 1.2
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]particle[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Spawns particles at the player's location.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: particle
  particle: VILLAGER_HAPPY
  count: 30
  offset-x: 0.5
  offset-y: 1.0
  offset-z: 0.5
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]title[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Displays a title and subtitle on screen. Durations in ticks (20 ticks = 1 second).
[CODE=YAML]
- type: title
  title: "<green>Thank you!"
  subtitle: "<gray>Your vote has been counted."
  fade-in: 10
  stay: 40
  fade-out: 10
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]teleport[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Teleports the player to specific coordinates.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: teleport
  world: "world"
  x: 0.5
  y: 65.0
  z: 0.5
  yaw: 0.0
  pitch: 0.0
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]composite[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Bundles multiple rewards into one. All nested rewards are granted together.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: composite
  rewards:
    - type: command
      command: "give {player} emerald 3"
      as-console: true
    - type: sound
      sound: ENTITY_PLAYER_LEVELUP
      volume: 1.0
      pitch: 1.0
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]choice[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Opens a selection GUI where the player picks one reward from a set of options.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: choice
  options:
    - type: item
      material: DIAMOND
      amount: 5
    - type: xp
      amount: 500
    - type: currency
      currency: "coins"
      amount: 1000
[/CODE]

[SIZE=3][COLOR=#9b59b6]custom[/COLOR][/SIZE]
Executes a custom reward handler registered by another plugin via the JExVote API.
[CODE=YAML]
- type: custom
  handler: "my_plugin:special_reward"
  data:
    key: "value"
[/CODE]
[/SPOILER]


