[LIST]
[*]Paper 1.20.4+ (or Folia)
[*]Java 21+
[/LIST]

[B]Optional (soft dependencies):[/B]
[LIST]
[*][B]JExEconomy[/B] — Enables the [ICODE]currency[/ICODE] reward type
[*][B]LuckPerms[/B] — Enables the [ICODE]permission[/ICODE] reward type (timed permissions, server-specific)
[*][B]PlaceholderAPI[/B] — Exposes vote placeholders for use in scoreboards, tab lists, etc.
[*][B]Vault[/B] — Economy fallback if JExEconomy is not installed
[/LIST]


